. program define distinct, rclass
  1.     syntax varname [if]
  2.     preserve
  3.         marksample touse
  4.         keep if `touse'
  5.         keep `varlist'
  6.         duplicates drop
  7.         quietly count
  8.         return scalar ndistinct = r(N)
  9.     restore
